01:12:19.084 --> 01:12:20.918
Stuff like that.

01:12:21.086 --> 01:12:23.713
- Interviewer: Was he charming?
- Williams: Oh, yes.

01:12:23.881 --> 01:12:26.799
- ♪ Would you ride on, ya ♪
- ♪ Ride on ♪

01:12:26.967 --> 01:12:29.761
- ♪ Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, mama, mama ♪
- ♪ Ride on... ♪

01:12:29.928 --> 01:12:31.929
Interviewer: Why were so many girls
