01:12:32.097 --> 01:12:34.891
Oh, my God. ( Laughs )

01:12:35.059 --> 01:12:37.643
You don't know Bob.

01:12:37.811 --> 01:12:39.395
That's a handsome guy.

01:12:39.563 --> 01:12:43.399
♪ I went down
to Piccadilly Circus... ♪

01:12:43.567 --> 01:12:45.526
Interviewer: People have
visions of women

01:12:45.694 --> 01:12:47.362
