01:12:47.529 --> 01:12:50.448
- Jesus. ( Laughing )
- Grabbing clothes.

01:12:50.616 --> 01:12:53.743
- Is it like that?
- No.

01:12:53.911 --> 01:12:56.537
Interviewer: Why was he so successful
with women?

01:12:56.705 --> 01:12:58.706
Because he was shy.

01:13:00.125 --> 01:13:02.460
Bob is not the womanizer

01:13:02.628 --> 01:13:05.296
