he was gonna die,

02:13:47.769 --> 02:13:50.563
and they was just...

02:13:50.731 --> 02:13:53.024
they just surrounded him.

02:13:55.360 --> 02:13:58.654
That's why Bob never write
a will, l feel.

02:13:58.822 --> 02:14:01.115
Bob never want to give up.

02:14:01.283 --> 02:14:03.534
