it's like you say,

02:14:03.702 --> 02:14:06.871
"Well, you know,
I'm checking in."

02:14:08.832 --> 02:14:10.624
So I think that was
one of the reasons.

02:14:10.792 --> 02:14:13.878
I think one of the reasons, too, is he's
not the type of person who would say,

02:14:14.046 --> 02:14:17.715
"Now, okay, l leave this
for Ziggy, Cedella."

02:14:17.883 --> 02:14:21.469
You know, like, divide up. And "Okay,
